 {"id":"franken_numpy-u1zf","title":"Investigate Beads integrity_check warnings on freshly rebuilt DBs","description":"`br doctor --json` reports `sqlite.integrity_check` warnings (`page ... is never used`) on the canonical `.beads/beads.db` and also on a freshly rebuilt temp DB imported from healthy JSONL. `br show`, `br sync --status`, and rollback-only write probes all succeed, so this may be a frankensqlite/br diagnostic issue rather than repo-local corruption. Reproduce in isolation and determine whether repair, vacuum/checkpoint, or upstream fix is required.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-31T03:03:44.813529433Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-31T03:06:45.143864391Z","closed_at":"2026-03-31T03:06:45.143561397Z","close_reason":"Rebuilt a fresh DB from JSONL, proved  +  clears the integrity_check warning, promoted the cleaned candidate non-destructively, then applied the same cleanup on the canonical path. {\"ok\":true,\"checks\":[{\"name\":\"jsonl.merge_artifacts\",\"status\":\"ok\"},{\"name\":\"gitignore.beads_inner\",\"status\":\"ok\"},{\"name\":\"sync_jsonl_path\",\"status\":\"ok\",\"message\":\"JSONL path is within sync allowlist\",\"details\":{\"path\":\"/data/projects/franken_numpy/.beads/issues.jsonl\",\"beads_dir\":\"/data/projects/franken_numpy/.beads\"}},{\"name\":\"sync_conflict_markers\",\"status\":\"ok\",\"message\":\"No merge conflict markers found\"},{\"name\":\"jsonl.parse\",\"status\":\"ok\",\"message\":\"Parsed 195 records\",\"details\":{\"path\":\"/data/projects/franken_numpy/.beads/issues.jsonl\",\"records\":195}},{\"name\":\"db.recovery_artifacts\",\"status\":\"ok\"},{\"name\":\"db.sidecars\",\"status\":\"warn\",\"message\":\"WAL sidecar exists without a matching SHM sidecar at /data/projects/franken_numpy/.beads/beads.db-wal (expected for frankensqlite)\",\"details\":{\"findings\":[\"WAL sidecar exists without a matching SHM sidecar at /data/projects/franken_numpy/.beads/beads.db-wal (expected for frankensqlite)\"]}},{\"name\":\"schema.tables\",\"status\":\"ok\",\"details\":{\"tables\":[\"issues\",\"dependencies\",\"labels\",\"comments\",\"events\",\"config\",\"metadata\",\"dirty_issues\",\"export_hashes\",\"child_counters\",\"blocked_issues_cache\"]}},{\"name\":\"schema.columns\",\"status\":\"ok\"},{\"name\":\"db.recoverable_anomalies\",\"status\":\"ok\"},{\"name\":\"db.null_defaults\",\"status\":\"ok\"},{\"name\":\"sqlite.integrity_check\",\"status\":\"ok\"},{\"name\":\"counts.db_vs_jsonl\",\"status\":\"ok\",\"message\":\"Both have 195 records\"},{\"name\":\"sync.metadata\",\"status\":\"ok\",\"message\":\"Database and JSONL are in sync\",\"details\":{\"dirty_issues\":0,\"last_import\":\"2026-03-31T03:05:34.386290282+00:00\",\"jsonl_hash\":\"0859c97149320955\"}},{\"name\":\"db.write_probe\",\"status\":\"ok\",\"message\":\"Rollback-only issue write succeeded for franken_numpy-070\"},{\"name\":\"sqlite3.integrity_check\",\"status\":\"warn\",\"message\":\"sqlite3 not available; skipping orthogonal integrity validation\"}]}, ✓ franken_numpy-i7vy · Fix root .gitignore so .beads inner ignore rules work   [● P1 · CLOSED]\nOwner: ubuntu · Type: bug\nCreated: 2026-03-31 · Updated: 2026-03-31\nClosed: 2026-03-31 (Removed the blanket root .beads/ ignore, preserved specific local-only Beads artifact ignores, and verified br doctor\nOK jsonl.merge_artifacts\nOK gitignore.beads_inner\nOK sync_jsonl_path: JSONL path is within sync allowlist\nOK sync_conflict_markers: No merge conflict markers found\nOK jsonl.parse: Parsed 195 records\nOK db.recovery_artifacts\nWARN db.sidecars: WAL sidecar exists without a matching SHM sidecar at /data/projects/franken_numpy/.beads/beads.db-wal (expected for frankensqlite)\nOK schema.tables\nOK schema.columns\nOK db.recoverable_anomalies\nOK db.null_defaults\nWARN sqlite.integrity_check: database disk image is malformed: page 53 is never used\nOK counts.db_vs_jsonl: Both have 195 records\nOK sync.metadata: Database and JSONL are in sync\nWARN db.write_probe: Failed to begin rollback-only write probe: database is busy\nWARN sqlite3.integrity_check: sqlite3 not available; skipping orthogonal integrity validation now reports gitignore.beads_inner=ok.)\n\n`br doctor` warns that root `.gitignore` excludes `.beads/`, which prevents `.beads/.gitignore` from governing Beads runtime artifacts. This conflicts with the repo workflow that stages `.beads/` state in git. Fix the root ignore rule so tracked Beads files are not globally suppressed while preserving ignores for local-only sidecars/history., and {\n  \"dirty_count\": 0,\n  \"last_import_time\": \"2026-03-31T03:05:34.386290282+00:00\",\n  \"jsonl_content_hash\": \"0859c97149320955dbb4ef60e675ca09401d1a8df82848f4e8a36d32182dd932\",\n  \"jsonl_exists\": true,\n  \"jsonl_newer\": false,\n  \"db_newer\": false\n} are now healthy on the default DB.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
